or\"></a> 只能拍摄的眼镜","id":"只能拍摄的眼镜","index":"5.9"}]},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> AR 应用场景","id":"ar-应用场景","index":"6","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 远程协作","id":"远程协作","index":"6.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 检修和维护","id":"检修和维护","index":"6.2"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 互动营销","id":"互动营销","index":"6.3"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 影音社交","id":"影音社交","index":"6.4"}]},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> AR 开发套件（Software Development Kit，SDK）","id":"ar-开发套件software-development-kitsdk","index":"7","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 通用 AR 开发套件","id":"通用-ar-开发套件","index":"7.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 人脸 AR 开发套件","id":"人脸-ar-开发套件","index":"7.2"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 网页 AR","id":"网页-ar","index":"7.3"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 行业标准","id":"行业标准","index":"7.4"}]},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 设计工具","id":"设计工具","index":"8","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 内容创作平台","id":"内容创作平台","index":"8.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 软件工具","id":"软件工具","index":"8.2"}]},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 游戏和影视","id":"游戏和影视","index":"9","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 游戏","id":"游戏","index":"9.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 影视","id":"影视","index":"9.2"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Bingo","link":"<a href=\"https://talk2.it/post/ar/\" title=\"AR、MR 设计资源导航 | v1.0\">https://talk2.it/post/ar/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}